%% WYVERN-E 4.0 — flight state machine (Pico 2 W, fins + active TVC)
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> BOOT
    BOOT: BOOT — mount SD, mux + init 3x BNO085 (Game Rotation Vector), baro datum
    ARMED: ARMED — RBF pulled; launch-detect primed; camera recording
    BOOST: BOOST — F15-4; 500 Hz TVC PID stabilize→maneuver; gimbal within ±5°
    COAST: COAST(brief) — burnout t=3.45s; NO thrust ⇒ NO TVC authority
    RECOVER: RECOVER — F15-4 motor ejection ~t=7.5s via bypass tube (FC logs only)
    DESCENT: DESCENT — 18in chute ~6 m/s; log to apogee+landing
    LANDED: LANDED — flush log, safe outputs
    BOOT --> ARMED: self-test pass
    ARMED --> BOOST: |a|>3g
    BOOST --> COAST: burnout (t>3.45s)
    COAST --> RECOVER: F15-4 ejection ~7.5s
    RECOVER --> DESCENT --> LANDED --> [*]
